chore: release v0.4.0

FIX: Profile parameter PV1 ... PV8 maximum value set to 9000 **_(Issue #24)_** `State objects PV1 ... PV8 need to be deleted first in order to be create correctly during adapter start`
========================================================================
ADD: [SafeFloor Device] New **SafeFloor Units** Tab in adapter settings to manage up to 4 **_SafeFloor Connect_** devices
ADD: New option **_"Hide all trigger info logging messages"_** in Tab **_"Advanced Options"_** to `hide all info logging messages at trigger events`
ADD: New option **_"Allow SERVICE and FACTORY state changes"_** in Tab **_"Advanced Options"_** to enable/disable changes of objects protected by the manufacturer
ADD: State `CLRALA` - **_DeviceControl State_** to clear current alarm and reopen main valve
ADD: State `BFT` - **_Button filter threshold_**
ADD: State `BPT` - **_Button proximity threshold_**
ADD: State `CNF` - **_Conductivity factor_**
ADD: State `CNL` - **_Conductivity limit_**
ADD: State `DBD` - **_MLT pressure drop_**
ADD: State `DBT` - **_MLT pressure drop time_**
ADD: State `DCM` - **_MLT test time close_**
ADD: State `DOM` - **_MLT test time open_**
ADD: State `DPL` - **_MLT pulses_**
ADD: State `DST` - **_MLT test time NOPULS_**
ADD: State `DTC` - **_MLT verification cycles_**
ADD: State `DTT` - **_Micro-Leakage-Test start time_**
ADD: State `HTD` - **_Disable HTTPS connection (only MQTT)_**
ADD: State `MQT` - **_MQTT connection type_**
ADD: State `MRT` - **_Maintenance (Husty) server connection_**
ADD: State `MSC` - **_MQTT reconnect time_**
ADD: State `DSV` - **_Micro-Leakage-Test state_**
ADD: State `FSL` - **_Paired Floorsensors list_**
ADD: State `ALH` - **_Alarm history file_**
ADD: State `STH` - **_Statistics history file_**
ADD: State `PAH` - **_Parameters history file_**
ADD: State `WFL` - **_WiFi scan_**
ADD: State `BUZ` - **_Buzzer parameters_**
ADD: State `ALM` - **_Alarm memory_**
ADD: State `TTM` - **_Turbine no pulse max. time_**
ADD: State `TYP` - **_Safe-Tec type_**
ADD: State `WNS` - **_WiFi AP disabled_**
ADD: State `HWV` - **_Hardware version_**
ADD: State `DKI` - **_Safe-Tec device kind ID_**
ADD: State `FSA` - **_Add (Pair) Floorsensor_**
ADD: State `WFK` - **_WiFi key_** After entering the WiFi key into the WFK state the key will be send to device and afterwards state value will be cleared imediatly
ADD: Device Control State `UPG` set to true initiates **_Firmware upgrase_** (only if new firmware is available)
ADD: Device Control State `DEX` set to 1 initiates **_MLT (Micro Leake Test)_**
ADD: Warn message in log if a new firmware for SafeTech Connect device is available
REM: Removed **_testing loop_** functionality
========================================================================
= The following objects need to be deleted first in order to get the new functionality
= Since objects will be checked and created only during startup of the adapter follow this procedure
= (stop wamo adapter -> delete state object -> start wamo -> object will be created)
========================================================================
CHG: State `ALD` - **_Alarm duration (signaling time)_** can now be changed by user
CHG: State `CLP` - **_Cluster Profile can_** now be changed by user
CHG: State `SLO` - **_Self learning offset_** can now be changed by user
CHG: State `SLP` - **_Self learning phase_** can now be changed by user
CHG: State `SMF` - **_Self learning minimum flow_** can now be changed by user
CHG: State `SOF` - **_Self learning offset flow_** can now be changed by user
CHG: State `TMZ` - **_Time zone_** can now be changed by user
CHG: State `WFC` - **_WiFi connect (SSID)_** can now be changed by user
CHG: State `71` - **_Leakage protection deactivated_** - State moved from **_Settings_** to **_Device-Control_** (please delete Object **_71_** in object _Settings_ folder )
CHG: State `71` - **_Leakage protection deactivated_** - is now changable (warn message appears in log if Leakage protection is deaktivated) 
========================================================================